{"tid":1457932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進：可以當場擊斃示威者","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:55:00.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9b86a1aacf0b5178a6d5d9d8eae68c79606db789","tid":1457932,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php4g4iCX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php4g4iCX.jpg&h=36a91fa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港警察武力鎮壓反送中人士，中國官媒《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進竟反過來指責示威者使用過度暴力，已到了可以當場被擊斃的程度。圖為港警逮捕示威民眾。（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港反送中運動日益遭到暴力鎮壓，昨（11日）港警不僅近距離開槍射爆女性眼睛，更在港鐵站投射催淚彈逮人。然而，中國官媒《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進竟反過來指責示威者使用過度暴力，已到了可以當場被擊斃的程度。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進在微博發表的文章被擷圖廣為轉發，可以看到他指責暴徒昨（11日）晚向港警投擲汽油彈，造成警察身體多處燒傷。胡錫進表示，香港民眾絕對不會支持這樣的行為，「這樣的暴行已經到了可以當場擊斃施暴者的惡劣程度」。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進說，他和《環球時報》強烈譴責以汽油彈攻擊警方的暴徒，更嗆聲「你們的那點力量在國家面前微不足道」，並勸示威者早點收手，否則「下場只會更糟」，言語間顯然充滿威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2881926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2881926&d=5%2F0N1eX%2FnGDFGLWAFE16zrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=0a918315\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2881926&h=947bb545\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2881926</a>"},{"pid":"95911b85d835ccc2e34f711277668bf88acf2a14","tid":1457932,"uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiokKv6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiokKv6.gif&h=b05ab9a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2f73efa0a17f950548c2d4fa27b6efa590ed212","tid":1457932,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"筆指揮槍？"},{"pid":"68d928e1bbf